      "review_summary": "The PR adds a right-click Reply affordance in the Control UI webchat with transient reply state, quote prepending, a custom context menu, and reply-preview styling.\n\nPR surface: Source +221. Total +221 across 5 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the PR defects: exact-head source shows the only production caller omits reply props while the handler requires onSetReply after preventDefault. The CSS regression is also source-reproducible by comparing current main's 12px/focus-visible baseline with the PR head.",
